description.value: A brief description of what MyIG is about (probably the same text as in your readme)

An Allergies/Adverse Reactions record contains one VAAllergyIntolerance. This resource may contain Provenance resources documenting the origination, verification, and assessment, and, if applicable, circumstances under which it was judged to be in error. The originating Practitioner includes a title.
